<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/index.css"/> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/shop.css"/>  
    <title>상품 등록 폼</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <a href="/"><img src="../images/TabbyPaws.svg" alt="TabbyPaws 로고"></a>
        <button id="login-link">
            <img src="../images/login_paw.svg" alt="로그인" class="login-paw-btn">
        </button>
    </header>
    <div id="profile-panel" class="profile-panel">
        <button class="close-btn" id="close-profile">닫기</button>
        <!-- 프로필 내용을 동적으로 삽입 -->
        <% if (isAuthenticated) { %>
            <div class="my_page">
                <a href="#" class="profile_img"></a>
                <p class="user_name"><%= user.name %>님</p> <!-- 사용자 ID 사용 -->
                </div>
            <ul class="my_link">
                <li><a href="">구매내역</a></li>
                <li><a href="">장바구니</a></li>
                <li><a href="">환불/교환 신청</a></li>
                <li><a href="">공지사항</a></li>
                <li><a href="">FAQ</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="modify_link">
                <li><a href="">회원정보 수정</a></li>
                <li><a href="">비밀번호 수정</a></li>
                <li><a href="">로그아웃</a></li>
            </ul>
        <% } else { %>
            <div class="login_page">
                <p><a href="/login">로그인</a> 후 이용가능합니다.</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="shop_container">
        <div class="link_container">
            <div class="link_check"><h2>상품이 등록되어있는 쇼핑몰 링크가 있으신가요?</h2><input type="checkbox"></div>
            <input type="text" placeholder="상품페이지가 연결된 쇼핑몰 링크를 등록해주세요">
        </div>
        <form action="/shop/add" method="post">
            <h3>상품 이미지 등록</h3>
            <input type="file">
            <h3>상품제목</h3>
            <input type="text" name="title">
            <h3>상품소개</h3>
            <textarea name="content"></textarea>
            <h3>상품 상세정보 <span>* 선택적 필수 사항</span></h3>
            <div>
                <p>알러지 성분 여부</p>
                <div class="aliergic_container">
                    <span>
                        <img src="../../images/chicken.svg">
                        <label>닭고기</label>
                        <input type="checkbox">
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <img src="../../images/beef.svg">
                        <label>소고기</label>
                        <input type="checkbox">
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <img src="../../images/fork.svg">
                        <label>돼지고기</label>
                        <input type="checkbox">
                    </span>
                    <span>
                        <img src="../../images/nuts.svg">
                        <label>견과류</label>
                        <input type="checkbox">
                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p>급여 권장연령</p>
                <select>
                    <option value="키튼">키튼</option>
                    <option value="성묘">성묘</option>
                    <option value="노묘">노묘</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div>
                <input type="checkbox">
            </div>
            <textarea name="ingredient"></textarea>
            <button>이미지추가</button>
            <input type="file">
        </form>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <ul> 
            <li><a href="/introduce">페이지 소개</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">사용자 이용약관</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">개인정보 처리방침</a></li>
            <li><a href="/faq">자주묻는 질문</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">contact</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p>email: tabby@naver.com</p>
        <p class="copywrite">© 2024 TabbyPaws ALL RIGHTS RESERVED</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>